<title>VEL IN A KA KHAMH CH444</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawlei donghnak a phan te lai, Ka hngalhnak bang ka tuah kho lo, Ka
 thawhthan tikah ka lawm lai, Kan Siangpahrang he ka um lai.

[C1]
   Hmaitonh in ka hmuh lai Vancung khua ah ka hmuh lai i, A vel
   in-khamhnak kha-fak pi-in ka aupi chin lai.

[V2]
 Vawlei umnak a rawk te lai, Zeitik a si lai ka hngal lo,
 Sihmanh-sehlaw a zungzal in, Vancung khua ah ka um te lai.

[C2]
   Hmaitonh in ka hmuh lai Vancung khua ah ka hmuh lai i, A vel
   in-khamhnak kha-fak pi-in ka aupi chin lai.

[V3]
 Ni ceunak kha a kih tikah, Bawipa he kan i tong te lai, Bawipa nawl
 bang na tuah ahcun, An luhter lai, dinhnak chungah.

[C3]
   Hmaitonh in ka hmuh lai Vancung khua ah ka hmuh lai i, A vel
   in-khamhnak kha-fak pi-in ka aupi chin lai.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
</song>